Dialogs.Dialog: This is not bad, I guess.
This is good. A feeling like this...
I also like this... I guess.
I've never felt like this before...
I'm glad to be with you.
Hey... The wicked one is you.
Do you really like doing this？
Do you think this is enjoyable？
The weather's nice and I feel good.
Hey, what do we do next？
Is it okay that I feel so good？
I want us to be like this forever.
You knew it but you still did this？ ...Hey.
...My face is turning red because of you.
It's only you who can do this.
Can I do the same to you too？
I wish we could stop the time here.
I want to stay like this...
Hehe. Can you be like this for a while？
This is not bad, I think.
I'm too happy that I feel scared.
Never leave me... Can you promise？
Don't do this to anyone else.
If you don't do this to anyone else, it's fine.
Keep looking at me. Only me.
What is it all of a sudden？
What do you think about me？
Have you thought about my feelings？
If you do this again, I won't forgive you.
What did you do to me...？
How can I make you understand？
I beg you. Please stop it.
Even if it's you, this is not good.
Hey, don't make me feel troubled.
I take good care of my hair, you know？
I kind of like it like this.
When you caress me, I feel sleepy.
Can I do the same thing to you？
Next time, just tell me. I'll fix it myself.
A little bit more. How's that？
I think it's better to stop this now...
I don't think I have any bed hair...
Hehe. Is there static electricity on my hair？
I'll fix it later. Oh well.
Can you be a bit gentler？
I feel like I'm a dog or a cat now.
It's not good to do this to others.
I had set my hair nicely, but...
I think I don't have a fever...
The spot you touched me becomes so warm.
It feels good when you touch me.
...I won't forgive you even if you apologize！
What？ Wanna tell me a secret？
You are not allowed to upset me.
Huh！？ Hey, don't do that, okay？
I'm not going to spoil you. No...
Wanna be like this for a while？ Okay, fine.
...Can I be near you like this？
Hehe. Shall I lean on you？
To walk arm in arm is a little...
I'm not in the mood for that now...
You can't do this to anyone else, okay？
I feel safe when you hold my hand...
It's good that we are lovers. Yeah...
It hurts. Can you let go of my hand？
Why are you trying to hold my hand？
I don't think this is good...
Why did you grab me like that？
Isn't the weather too hot to get close like this？
It's so hot. I can let you be near me for a while though.
Isn't it hot？ If you feel okay, then it's fine.
Your sweat？ I don't mind about that.
My heart is throbbing when you get close... Is it because of the hot weather？
Isn't it hot？ But I won't let you go▼
It feels good despite the hot weather... Isn't it mysterious？
Can I get some warmth from your body heat？ Oh well.
I don't need you to act as my windbreaker.
I'll hold your hand until you feel warm, okay？
If we get close to each other, we won't feel cold, right？
If you hold me tighter, you'll feel warmer.
Don't get away from me, okay？
...I'm getting confused. What are you doing？
I feel safe because you're near me.
Don't touch me in a weird spot.
This is special... just for you.
Hey... Why did you do that？
Do you think you can do anything with me？
Hey, you don't have to hurry like that.
Hehe. Should I rely on you？
I won't let any insect bite you▼
Is it okay to let me walk alone？
I wonder if I should take this seriously...
I don't know if anyone's watching us...
You don't want to get lost？ Okay, then.
If we do this, we won't get lost, right？
Hey, do I look like a kid？
Are you nervous？ Actually, me too.
When we get in the water, you won't leave me, right？
Why did you do that all of a sudden？
I'm not looking away. I'm not like you though...
I'm going to shrink if you stare at me like that.
Is my nose growing longer or something？
My arm？ I don't mind though.
This is your girlfriend's privilege, right？
I want to be like this forever... Maybe.
Okay, I lend my arm to you.
If we go arm in arm, is it hard to walk？
This is a little bit too embarrassing.
If it's just a little bit...
...Sometimes, it's nice to be treated like a kid.
Don't let go of me. Never.
I don't quite like this... I think.
We have arrived now. So I'm okay.
Um, seems like you can't calm down.
Is the way I walk different from usual？
Hey, don't look at me like that.
Isn't it a little too sexy...？
Is the way I walk strange？
What is it？ I don't understand.
Hey, aren't you staring at me too much？
If anything worries you, tell me.
I'll have a nice sleep tonight, I think.
Can you comfort me a bit？ I don't want to go home.
Hehe. Can I touch you too？
I really don't want to go home...
Of course, it feels good when you touch me.
You touched me gently... I love that...
We'll see each other again soon, right...？
Can we go somewhere else after this？ Hmm.
...Yeah. I want to stay like this...
What can I do？ I don't want to leave...
I want to stay like this...
Can I stay closer to you...？ Hmm.
I want to forget about my curfew...
Will you not let me go？ ...I'd be happy.
I was thinking about touching you. Hehe.
Can we be like this forever？
You like touching my hair？ I see...
My forehead？ Hehe. It's okay here.
Our hands touched... Um, it's good.
Touching someone's hair is special, right？
I don't mind you touching my hair...
It's okay if you touch me... I like it.
My forehead...？ I can be defenseless like this in front of you...
Is my forehead hot？ It's because you touched me there...
When you touch my forehead, I feel very happy. Because it's you...
My ears are very sensitive... Now I can feel your touch...
My ears became very hot because you touched them...
Does it feel good to touch my ear？ Hehe.
Want to hold my arm？ ...Fine. Just never leave me then...
I can't go against you when you touch my arm like this...
I've always thought about hugging you with these arms...
When you grab my hand, you grab my heart as well...
My hands are happiest when you're holding them...
Can you grab my hand tighter？ I don't want to forget this touch even after you let go of it.
